####################
# Test that I find all the markers in a file
####################

Given (Some text with no markers in it):
  hello
  this is in the fold
  this is outside of the fold

Execute (Remove the folds [there are none]):
  call RemoveMarkers()

Expect (Nothing changed):
  hello
  this is in the fold
  this is outside of the fold


Given (Some text with a single set of markers in it):
  first line
  {{{
  this was in a fold
  }}}
  no longer in a fold

Execute (Remove the folds):
  call RemoveMarkers()

Expect (Folds removed):
  first line
  this was in a fold
  no longer in a fold

Given (Some text with embedded markers in it):
  first line
  {{{
    second line
    {{{
      more folds!
    }}}
    first fold again
  }}}
  outside of folds

Execute (Remove the nested folds):
  call RemoveMarkers()

Expect (Nested folds removed):
  first line
    second line
      more folds!
    first fold again
  outside of folds


